        <div class="question">


            <div class="welovestackoverflow" style="margin-top: 10px;">
                <div style="float: left;">
                        <p>
Sinatra is a Domain Specific Language (DSL) for quickly creating web applications in Ruby with minimal effort. It is an alternative to other Ruby web application frameworks such as Ruby on Rails, Merb, Nitro, Camping, and Rango.                         </p>
                                            <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">
                            <a title="tag wiki" href="/tags/sinatra/info">learn more&hellip;</a>
                            <span class="lsep">|</span> 
                            <a title="top answerers and askers in this tag" href="/tags/sinatra/topusers">top users</a> 
                            <span class="lsep">|</span> 
                            <a title="common, alternate spellings or phrasings for this tag" href="/tags/sinatra/synonyms">synonyms</a>
                                                    </p>
                </div>
